# |<----  Using a maximum of 72 characters  ---->|

# Explain why this change was made (optional, wrap at 72 chars):


# --- Conventional Commits cheat sheet ---
# Types:  feat | fix | refactor | chore | docs | test | style | perf
# Scope:  the module or area touched, e.g. timesheet, sync-queue, profile
#
# Example:
#   feat(profile): add language toggle to settings row
#
#   Crew leaders asked to switch languages without opening the app's
#   system settings; this exposes the existing LanguageProvider toggle
#   directly on the Profile screen.
